# ArbitrageRadar — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (local dev) and/or set the same variable in
# your Vercel project (Settings -> Environment Variables).
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERPAPI_KEY — enables LIVE data (real Google Trends interest-over-time).
#
#   • Get a key: https://serpapi.com/manage-api-key  (free tier = 100 searches/mo)
#   • When set, each product's 7-day demand series is pulled live from Google
#     Trends for its primary keyword.
#   • When UNSET, the app serves the curated demo dataset (and shows a
#     "DEMO DATA" badge). It never crashes without a key.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SERPAPI_KEY=
